PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Deputy Prime Minister, Minister of Finance and Minister of Infrastructure, who continues to have responsibility for the control and supervision of the Royal Canadian Mint under Order in Council P.C. 2002-28 of January 15, 2002, of TIMOTHY SPIEGEL of Kelowna, British Columbia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Royal Canadian Mint to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
